This page displayes the following participation flows:

cleanup
- registered: come back to this page, once the cleanup has started in order to participate
- started: google maps integration, timer, zigarettencounter, etc.
- ended: thanks for participation, summary of the cleanup: zigarettencounter, distance, time, etc.

PARTICIPATION STATUS: <%= @participation.status %>

<% if @participation.status == "registered" %>

  <h1>Clicke auf starten, um das CleanUp zu beginnen.</h1>
  <%= form_with url: participation_path(@participation), method: :patch, local: true do |f| %>
    <%= f.hidden_field :participation_action, value: "start" %>
    <%= f.submit "Starten" %>
  <% end %>

<% elsif @participation.status == "started" %>

  <h1>Das CleanUp läuft. Klicke auf beenden, um das CleanUp zu beenden.</h1>
  <%= form_with url: participation_path(@participation), method: :patch, local: true do |f| %>
    <%= f.hidden_field :participation_action, value: "return" %>
    <%= f.submit "Beenden" %>
  <% end %>

<% elsif @participation.status == "ended" %>

  <h1>Vielen Dank für deine Teilnahme!</h1>

<% end %>
